/2020/03/%e3%80%90%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%93%ad%e5%a2%99%e3%80%91%e6%9d%8e%e5%8c%bb%e7%94%9f-%e4%bd%a0%e8%bf%99%e8%be%b9%e4%bb%bf%e4%bd%9b%e6%88%90%e4%ba%86%e5%a4%a7%e5%ae%b6%e8%af%b4%e5%bf%83%e9%87%8c%e8%af%9d/\">【中国哭墙】李医生 你这边仿佛成了大家说心里话的地方（3月16日）</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【中国哭墙】李医生 你这边仿佛成了大家说心里话的地方（3月16日）》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e3%80%90%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%93%ad%e5%a2%99%e3%80%91%e6%9d%8e%e5%8c%bb%e7%94%9f-%e4%bd%a0%e8%bf%99%e8%be%b9%e4%bb%bf%e4%bd%9b%e6%88%90%e4%ba%86%e5%a4%a7%e5%ae%b6%e8%af%b4%e5%bf%83%e9%87%8c%e8%af%9d/embed/#?secret=ocoHuWDMUl\" data-secret=\"ocoHuWDMUl\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":998,"categories":[18271,38912,39924,17016],"tags":[39920,39775,39753,39648]}